parameters:
Student Council Member: President Memimi, it's almost time
for the school assembly. Shall we head to the gymnasium?
Hehe...

Memimi: (All the students at the academy know that I've
become an AV actress... And of course, they've seen me in
all sorts of embarrassing situations because of weird
campaigns and whatnot... As the student council president...
I have to be firm, but...)

Memimi: ...I'm sorry, I feel... a bit unable to speak
properly... Maybe you guys could take over for me...

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: What's this, you're still here?! Hurry
up and get to the school assembly, we're about to start
filming the AV! All the students will be extras... Make sure
they get a good look!
